    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年10月13日-2025年10月17日）",
    "followRuleId": "1295324199100104704",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1295590753419149312\">《京东开放平台安心驼奶粉品质认证标准》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确适用范围、相关术语及定义、上线权益、认证要求、监管要求等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1296306000765476864\">《京东开放平台草饲牛奶品质认证标准》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确适用范围、相关术语及定义、上线权益、认证要求、监管要求等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1295654339739017216\">《京东开放平台商家服务管理规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）增加&ldquo;售后服务承诺与平台服务产品不一致&rdquo;的违规场景。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">）&ldquo;售后处理不规范&rdquo;违规场景的处理措施增加：预警整改，下架违规商品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1289863613818167296\">《京东开放平台大时尚品类新商激励政策》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在政策周期内，满足GMV考核目标的商家可获得广告金激励。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1290142210806145024\">《京东开放平台企业店铺&ldquo;老带新&rdquo;招商激励政策》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在政策周期内，老商家推荐新商家入驻POP-SOP模式后，新商入驻首月或下个自然月店铺维度首次达到成交单量&ge;30单或成交GMV&ge;3万元，则推荐其入驻的老商家可获得500元广告虚拟金。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1290142910080368640\">《京东开放平台个人/个体店铺&ldquo;老带新&rdquo;招商激励政策》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #0563c1; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=882901586832134144\">《京东开放平台咚咚热情掌柜服务规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">新增金牌客服服务质检标准及对应的细则，并修订金牌客服认证的方式及标准。</span></p>",
